OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey's public
OL,7,Fspending is too high, according to the
OL,8,Fisland's most senior civil servant.
OL,10,FDr Andrew McLaughlin has criticised
OL,11,Fthe States' decision to approve #1.28
OL,12,Fbillion of public services funding in
OL,13,Fits 2026 Budget.
OL,15,FSpeaking to the Public Accounts
OL,16,FCommittee, Dr McLaughlin said: "I
OL,17,Fgenuinely struggle to understand why
OL,18,Fthe public service has to spend more
OL,19,Fthan #1 billion to run in Jersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"So that means to me, there's a couple
OL,7,Fof hundred million (pounds) which
OL,8,Fmight be best going into reserves and
OL,9,Fthen doing stuff when you have to."
OL,11,FDr McLaughlin added that the
OL,12,FGovernment "takes on stuff it probably
OL,13,Fdoesn't have the budgets or the
OL,14,Fcapacities to do really well and it
OL,15,Fturns into operational risk".
OL,17,FHe explained: "Let's take the Fire
OL,18,FService - we've adopted, effectively,
OL,19,FUK fire standards in all shapes and
OL,20,Fforms.
OL,26,@oD@TpmoD@[pn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"It's quite difficult for such a small
OL,7,Ffire service in such a small island to
OL,8,Ftranspose UK-generated standards into
OL,9,Four environment.
OL,11,F"In order for them to do that, they
OL,12,Ftherefore have to access resources,
OL,13,Fmoney to put that in place."
OL,15,FDr McLaughlin stated: "When you're a
OL,16,Fsmall island economy, which,
OL,17,Fremarkably, has grown this #4 billion
OL,18,Ffinance centre on it, it's actually
OL,19,Fquite difficult to compare yourself to
OL,20,Fother people.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"This is really important, because
OL,7,Fthis obsession with comparative
OL,8,Fanalysis, rather than sitting back and
OL,9,Fsaying 'what have we got here? Who are
OL,10,Fwe? What have we got? How can we earn
OL,11,Four keeping in the world?' It's Oscar
OL,12,FWilde - be yourself."
OL,14,FReacting to Dr McLaughlin's comments,
OL,15,Feconomist Dr Michael Oliver added:
OL,16,F"What he's saying is very serious.
OL,17,FSpending seems to be out of control,
OL,18,Fthere's no accountability and no
OL,19,Fvision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"We're spending like a big country, as
OL,7,Fhe said, but to what purpose? Are we
OL,8,Fdoing things in Jersey that we don't
OL,9,Fhave to do? Why aren't we working with
OL,10,Four neighbour? What actually are we
OL,11,Fdoing in Government that leads to this
OL,12,Fhuge expenditure which, of course, the
OL,13,Ftaxpayer has to fund?"
OL,15,FWhile Guernsey is undertaking a review
OL,16,Fof its tax system as its politicians
OL,17,Fgrapple with its #48 million black
OL,18,Fhole, Dr Oliver says Jersey's elected
OL,19,Fofficials will have equally hard
OL,20,Fdecisions to make.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,FHe explained: "Jersey seems reluctant
OL,7,Fto talk about tax at all.
OL,9,F"I think one of the clear messages has
OL,10,Fto be that whoever is in government
OL,11,Fafter June this year is going to have
OL,12,Fsome extremely difficult choices."
OL,14,FThis year, the health department is
OL,15,Freceiving more funding than any other,
OL,16,Fwith a budget of #381 million agreed
OL,17,Fby the States.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,FThe Government is also committed to
OL,7,Fspending #1 billion on building the
OL,8,Fnew hospital at Overdale over the next
OL,9,Ffour years.
OL,11,FPolitical commentator Susana Rowles
OL,12,Funderstands that some people want to
OL,13,Fbe assured the Government will not cut
OL,14,Ffunding to vital services, but
OL,15,Fbelieves the current level of public
OL,16,Fsector spending is "unsustainable".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,FShe said: "We need to have a really
OL,7,Fhonest conversation. The last three
OL,8,FChief Ministers have all said they
OL,9,Fwere going to curb public spending but
OL,10,Fit's very difficult to do that because
OL,11,Fon the frontline, people want their
OL,12,Fspecific service, they want that to
OL,13,Fcontinue, and people don't want to
OL,14,Flose access to anything they've
OL,15,Falready got.
OL,17,F"We need to have a really grown-up
OL,18,Fconversation with the voters this time
OL,19,Faround so that people actually get to
OL,20,Fthe issue here.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"We cannot spend money we haven't got
OL,7,Fand we need to start saving because
OL,8,FJersey is an island economy and it
OL,9,Fcannot print its own money.
OL,11,F"Therefore, it is so vulnerable to
OL,12,Fexternal pressures. We've got wars
OL,13,Fgoing on at the moment, the impact of
OL,14,Fwhich will be felt in our island, and
OL,15,Fwe need to have stabilisation funds
OL,16,Fand we need to have a strategic
OL,17,Freserve that enables us to actually go
OL,18,Four own way on things. Covid was an
OL,19,Fexample of that.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"We need to learn lessons from the
OL,7,Fpast."
OL,9,FIn response, Jersey's Chief Minister,
OL,10,FDeputy Lyndon Farnham, said: "There's
OL,11,Fa lot of accountability. We have
OL,12,Fstrict rules around how we manage our
OL,13,Ffinances. The Government are
OL,14,Faccountable to the States Assembly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"We've managed to significantly reduce
OL,7,Fthe growth in government expenditure.
OL,8,FWe have to double down. For example,
OL,9,Fthe growth when we took over in 2022-
OL,10,F23 was running at about 6% per annum.
OL,11,FIn 2025, in real terms, expenditure
OL,12,Fgrew by 1.25%. In 2026, the forecast
OL,13,Fis 2.5% so we've made a start, but
OL,14,Fwe've got to double down even further.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773072684
OL,3,CJersey spending too much 'like a big
OL,4,Ccountry', says top civil servant
OL,6,F"We've had to deal with very high
OL,7,Finflation over the last three years.
OL,8,FIt peaked, I think in 2023, at around
OL,9,F10%. It takes time to turn the ship
OL,10,Faround. We've made good progress and
OL,11,Fwe're heading in the right direction
OL,12,Funder Andrew McLoughlin's leadership.
OL,14,F"Had we not acted in the way we have,
OL,15,Fwe wouldn't have presented a #1.28
OL,16,Fbillion budget; it would have been
OL,17,Fmore like #1.4 billion."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
